    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend adventure, this car runs smoothly and is ready for its next chapter. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
