    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This F87-generation M2 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the N55 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-six mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The powertrain is mechanically sound, delivering consistent boost pressure and linear torque through the Active M Differential, which provides exceptional lateral stability and corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, utilizing M-specific aluminum suspension components and a subframe-mounted steering rack for high-fidelity feedback. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system pressure test and a fluid analysis to ensure the integrity of the high-performance oil system. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its history, the vehicle is free of structural modifications and retains its factory-engineered balance. A compelling, well-sorted example of BMW\u2019s most agile modern platform.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
