    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a discerning driver who values mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic. Finished in a timeless exterior that retains its deep gloss, the car has been meticulously garaged and serviced according to all manufacturer intervals. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of quality; the premium upholstery shows only light, natural creasing, and every electronic feature\u2014from the crisp infotainment display to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions flawlessly. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use, the body is straight and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. The engine delivers smooth, responsive power, and the transmission shifts with factory-spec precision. Recent maintenance includes a fresh fluid service and a new set of all-season tires, ensuring this car is ready for the road immediately. It is a reliable, sophisticated, and turnkey example for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
